
# COCKTAIL EXTRAVAGANZA
#### DATE: 2024/04/10
#### By *Lang'at Joel*
# Description
Welcome to Cocktail Extravaganza, a web application that allows you to explore a world of delightful cocktail recipes! Whether you're looking to discover new drinks or find a specific cocktail, Cocktail Extravaganza has got you covered.
# Features
Fetch Random Cocktail: Click the "Get Random Cocktail" button to fetch a random cocktail recipe and learn how to make it.
Search for Cocktails: Use the search bar to search for cocktails based on keywords. Enter the name or ingredients of the cocktail you're craving, and Cocktail Explorer will find it for you.
Detailed Cocktail Information: Each cocktail recipe comes with detailed information, including its name, image, and instructions on how to prepare it.
